OL,3,CJurgen Klopp confirmed as new Germany
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FJurgen Klopp has been confirmed as the
OL,7,Fnew head coach of the German men's
OL,8,Ffootball team.
OL,10,FThe former Liverpool manager, who has
OL,11,Fsigned a four-year contract, was the
OL,12,Ffirst man the German Football
OL,13,FAssociation (DFB) turned to when
OL,14,FJulian Nagelsmann resigned after
OL,15,FGermany's shock World Cup defeat by
OL,16,FParaguay in the last 32.
OL,18,FSpeaking at a press conference, Klopp
OL,19,Fmade it clear he would quit if the
OL,20,Fmedia invades his family privacy.
OL,26,@kD@BxznD@Bxz
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
