OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784909938
OL,3,CJurgen Klopp confirmed as new Germany
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FHe said: "I'm not doing this job for
OL,7,Fmyself. I'm doing it for you. I'm
OL,8,Ftaking this job even though I've seen
OL,9,Fhow you've treated Julian Nagelsmann
OL,10,Fand Thomas Tuchel.
OL,12,F"If tomorrow Jurgen Klopp is s*** then
OL,13,FI will be gone. But if the DFB says
OL,14,F'Come on, let's discontinue the job'
OL,15,Fthen that is it.
OL,17,F"And if you behave badly and don't
OL,18,Fleave my family in peace I will be
OL,19,Fgone, I'll just turn away. I love this
OL,20,Fjob, but I'm always ready to call it
OL,21,Fquits."
OL,26,@kD@BxztD@Oxz
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
