OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784909938
OL,3,CJurgen Klopp confirmed as new Germany
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FThe 59-year-old was appointed head of
OL,7,Fglobal soccer at Red Bull six months
OL,8,Fafter his exit from Liverpool, and
OL,9,Fstated that he had no desire to return
OL,10,Fto club management.
OL,12,FKlopp's release from his job at Red
OL,13,FBull was secured by the DFB making a
OL,14,Fone million euros donation to the
OL,15,Fcompany's Wings for Life foundation
OL,16,Fand agreeing to play three
OL,17,Finternationals in Leipzig in 2030.
OL,26,@kD@Bxz
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784909938
OL,3,CJurgen Klopp confirmed as new Germany
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FHe added, "What we need to achieve is
OL,7,Fmore intensity, more running, more
OL,8,Fdedication: counter-pressing has
OL,9,Falways been a key for me.
OL,11,F"Jurgen Klopp doesn't automatically
OL,12,Fmean we are going to be world
OL,13,Fchampions. Success is performance
OL,14,Fversus expectations. I think we need a
OL,15,Fnew set of expectations.
OL,17,F"We will leave no stone unturned, if
OL,18,Fthere is anything to be adapted,
OL,19,Fchanged or deleted I will do exactly
OL,20,Fthat."
OL,26,@kD@BxzsD@Cxz
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
