PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784909938
OL,3,CJurgen Klopp confirmed as new Germany
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FKlopp will be joined by two of his
OL,7,Fformer Liverpool assistants Pep
OL,8,FLijnders and Peter Krawietz, along
OL,9,Fwith Sven Bender who played under
OL,10,FKlopp at Borussia Dortmund also
OL,11,Fjoining.
OL,13,FHe won the Champions League, Premier
OL,14,FLeague, Club World Cup, FA Cup and
OL,15,FLeague Cup twice during his nine years
OL,16,Fat Liverpool.
OL,26,@kD@Bxz
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
