PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784909938
OL,3,CJurgen Klopp confirmed as new Germany
OL,4,Chead coach
OL,6,FHe pledged to be more sympathetic to
OL,7,Fclub managers and said: "If someone
OL,8,Fsays 'You can't call him and because
OL,9,Fhe has done four matches in a row' I
OL,10,Fwill say 'fine'," he said.
OL,12,F"I will not fight tooth and nail for
OL,13,Fthat player, I will listen to the club
OL,14,Fcoach."
OL,16,FHis first game in charge is against
OL,17,Fthe Netherlands in the Nations League
OL,18,Fon 24 September.
OL,26,@kD@BxzrD@QO]
